<item>
            <title>[LU-15388] Wrong dotdot FID parameter for osd_add_dot_dotdot()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15388</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Wrong FID has been passed to osd_add_dot_dotdot() and osd_add_dot_dotdot_internal(). Thus the FID of current directory is saved to &quot;..&quot; entry, not the parent directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
